<sn><md>### **Optative Sentence**
---
To express Blessing,Curse,Wish

It is a part of exclamatory sentence.

**Structure** : 
- May + sub + v1 ! or
- May + sub + v1 . (both are right)

#### **Example**
- May God bless you !
- May you rot in hell .</md></sn><config style="display:none"><tags>#07.optative sentence</tags><thumbnail></thumbnail><heading></heading><udate>Sat Jul 19 2025 08:21:51 GMT+0600 (Bangladesh Standard Time)</udate><id>article-B7IpFgCWHF</id><duration></duration></config>